{
  "page": "Wylla (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Wylla\" title=\"Wylla\">Wylla</a></b> is a wet nurse in service to House Dayne.\n</p><p>Other characters named <b>Wylla</b> include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_Fenn\" title=\"Wylla Fenn\">Wylla Fenn</a>, the mother of Lord Brandon Stark's bastard son Lonnel Snow.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_Manderly\" title=\"Wylla Manderly\">Wylla Manderly</a>, the daughter of Ser Wylis Manderly and Leona Woolfield.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Wylla_of_Wyl\" title=\"Wylla of Wyl\">Wylla of Wyl</a>, a warrior-maid of House Wyl who fought in the Battle by the Bloody Pool.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405111856\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.002 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:24248-0!canonical and timestamp 20260405111856 and revision id 314065\n -->\n",
